title: Catz [RC3X41] (wbfs)
description:
Catz

  Take care of your kitty by feeding, nursing and playing with him and see how the moods will change. Both cats, toys and environments are fully in 3D which makes it look much more natural. Have fun with your kitty by seeing through the eyes of your cat with the helmet camera or taking pictures in all sort of fantastic themed backdrops.
